1
00:00:08,466 --> 00:00:10,066
-[ GRUNTS ]

2
00:00:11,433 --> 00:00:13,033
-HUH?
-HE GOT US!

3
00:00:13,066 --> 00:00:14,300
-NOT QUITE!

4
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,100
-NUTS!

5
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,966
-SAY HELLO TO MY LOWER HALF!

6
00:00:23,266 --> 00:00:24,733
-HEY!
-HEY!

7
00:00:24,766 --> 00:00:27,033
-WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF THAT ZOMBINATION?

8
00:00:27,066 --> 00:00:29,033
-WHAT'S THAT?
YOU WANT TO SEE MORE?

9
00:00:29,066 --> 00:00:32,333
WELL, IF YOU INSIST!
-WELL, IF YOU INSIST!

10
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:35,200
ONE CAN OF WHUP ASS TO GO.

11
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:37,100
-COME BACK ANY TIME!

12
00:00:38,366 --> 00:00:41,400
OKAY, BOSS, WHAT DO YOU WANT US
TO DO WITH HIM NOW?

13
00:00:41,433 --> 00:00:43,200
-YOU KNOW THE DRILL.
LOCK HIM UP.

14
00:00:43,233 --> 00:00:44,800
-WILL DO, MA'AM!

15
00:00:44,833 --> 00:00:46,933
ALL RIGHT. YOU TAKE THE LEGS.

16
00:00:46,966 --> 00:00:48,166
-AGAIN?
-[ Thinking ] <i>FUYUMI...</i>

17
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,800
-I ALWAYS GET STUCK
WITH THE LEGS.

18
00:00:49,833 --> 00:00:51,433
<i>-...AT THE RATE</i>
<i>THINGS ARE GOING NOW,</i>

19
00:00:51,466 --> 00:00:52,966
<i>I MIGHT DIE</i>

20
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,433
<i>BEFORE I CAN</i>
<i>BRING YOU BACK TO LIFE.</i>

21
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,700
-[ SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

22
00:02:32,905 --> 00:02:35,871
-HUH.

23
00:02:35,905 --> 00:02:37,638
FASCINATING.

24
00:02:37,671 --> 00:02:40,471
I'M WELL AWARE OF GHOSTS,
BUT SHE APPEARS

25
00:02:40,505 --> 00:02:42,771
TO BE COMBINED
WITH ANOTHER KIND OF DEMON.

26
00:02:42,805 --> 00:02:44,238
-ANOTHER KIND?

27
00:02:44,271 --> 00:02:45,671
-WAIT, YOU MEAN LIKE...

28
00:02:45,705 --> 00:02:47,371
A VAMPIRE, RIGHT?
-A VAMPIRE, RIGHT?

29
00:02:47,405 --> 00:02:48,638
-IT APPEARS THAT WAY.

30
00:02:48,671 --> 00:02:50,138
-THAT FREAKIN' PERV!

31
00:02:50,171 --> 00:02:51,338
AND AFTER ALL THAT CRAP

32
00:02:51,371 --> 00:02:52,638
ABOUT NOT BEING INTERESTED
IN HER!

33
00:02:52,671 --> 00:02:55,338
-WAIT. YOU MEAN
SHE'S EATING FOR TWO NOW?

34
00:02:55,371 --> 00:02:57,405
GOT A BUN IN THE OVEN?
BAGGAGE IN THE BELLY?

35
00:02:57,438 --> 00:02:58,438
SHE'S KNOCKED UP?!

36
00:02:58,471 --> 00:03:00,205
-QUIT JUMPING TO CONCLUSIONS.

37
00:03:00,238 --> 00:03:02,538
I WAS TALKING ABOUT
THE MAGIC INSIDE OF HER.

38
00:03:02,571 --> 00:03:04,538
OUR BODY GENERATES IT

39
00:03:04,571 --> 00:03:06,438
BY ABSORBING THE MAGICAL ESSENCE

40
00:03:06,471 --> 00:03:08,738
THAT FILLS THE AIR
IN THE DEMON WORLD.

41
00:03:08,771 --> 00:03:11,405
EACH SPECIES OF DEMON
ONLY PRODUCES MAGIC

42
00:03:11,438 --> 00:03:15,138
THAT'S SPECIFIC TO THEIR KIND,
AND NO OTHER.

43
00:03:15,171 --> 00:03:16,838
BUT THIS GIRL'S BODY CONTAINS

44
00:03:16,871 --> 00:03:20,105
MAGIC FROM ANOTHER RACE,
MIXED IN WITH HER OWN,

45
00:03:20,138 --> 00:03:23,138
WHICH IS WHY HER LEGS
ARE BEGINNING TO DISAPPEAR.

46
00:03:23,171 --> 00:03:25,205
HER BODY IS OVERLOADED.

47
00:03:25,238 --> 00:03:27,105
A GHOST IS UNABLE TO PROCESS

48
00:03:27,138 --> 00:03:30,205
THE AMOUNT OF MAGICAL ESSENCE
REQUIRED FOR A VAMPIRE'S POWER.

49
00:03:30,238 --> 00:03:33,305
-OKAY, SO, IN OTHER WORDS,
THIS IS ALL STAZ'S FAULT?

50
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:36,105
-SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD DO, DOCTOR?

51
00:03:36,138 --> 00:03:39,871
-WITH ALL OF HER POTENTIAL,
SHE MAY BE ABLE TO RIVAL HIM.

52
00:03:39,905 --> 00:03:43,738
-I'M NOT CERTAIN HOW SHE COULD
HAVE ACQUIRED IT, EXACTLY,

53
00:03:43,771 --> 00:03:47,738
BUT IF SHE'S ABLE TO GET ANOTHER
DOSE OF MAGIC FROM A VAMPIRE...

54
00:03:47,771 --> 00:03:49,205
-HMM.
-HMM.

55
00:03:49,238 --> 00:03:51,505
-...THEN SHE COULD TAKE
EVERY LAST OUNCE

56
00:03:51,538 --> 00:03:55,438
AND HAVE ENOUGH MAGIC INSIDE HER
TO TOTALLY SEIZE CONTROL OF ONE.

57
00:03:55,471 --> 00:03:57,105
-HUH?

58
00:03:58,138 --> 00:03:59,671
[ BUZZER ]
-OH, GIVE IT UP, MAN!

59
00:03:59,705 --> 00:04:01,671
-YOU CAN'T WIN!
-IT'LL ALWAYS END THE SAME WAY!

60
00:04:03,238 --> 00:04:04,805
-WAIT.
-SERIOUSLY?

61
00:04:04,838 --> 00:04:06,071
YOU AGAIN?

62
00:04:06,105 --> 00:04:08,271
-AND STAY OUT!

63
00:04:08,305 --> 00:04:09,571
-[ <i>GROWLS</i> ]

64
00:04:09,605 --> 00:04:11,771
<i>-HUH? AAH! A BEAR!</i>
<i>IT'S A BEAR! NO!</i>

65
00:04:11,805 --> 00:04:14,371
-DRINKING COFFEE
WITH YOUR MASK ON?

66
00:04:14,405 --> 00:04:16,438
-[ GASPS ]

67
00:04:16,471 --> 00:04:19,338
-WHY ARE YOU SO SURPRISED
TO SEE ME?

68
00:04:19,371 --> 00:04:23,338
IS MY COMING TO VISIT
REALLY SO UNEXPECTED, LIZ?

69
00:04:23,371 --> 00:04:24,538
-BROTHER.

70
00:04:24,571 --> 00:04:26,638
N-NO. THIS IS HOT COCOA!

71
00:04:26,671 --> 00:04:28,605
-OH, THAT'S RIGHT.

72
00:04:28,638 --> 00:04:31,338
YOU DON'T LIKE
BITTER THINGS, DO YOU?

73
00:04:31,371 --> 00:04:32,638
SORRY. I HAD FORGOTTEN.

74
00:04:32,671 --> 00:04:34,471
BUT LIZ...

75
00:04:34,505 --> 00:04:37,671
THAT'S NOT THE ONLY REASON WHY
YOU LOOK SO NERVOUS, IS IT?

76
00:04:37,705 --> 00:04:39,138
-[ SIGHS ]

77
00:04:39,171 --> 00:04:40,838
-IN YOU GO!
-[ GRUNTS ]

78
00:04:40,871 --> 00:04:42,405
-AND DON'T YOU COME BACK!

79
00:04:42,438 --> 00:04:44,605
-'CAUSE IF YOU DO,
WE'LL KILL YOU, GOT IT?

80
00:04:44,638 --> 00:04:46,438
-YEAH!
I'M GETTING SICK OF THIS.

81
00:04:46,471 --> 00:04:48,338
[ BUZZER ]

82
00:04:48,371 --> 00:04:51,371
<i>-PRISONER NUMBER 1097639</i>

83
00:04:51,405 --> 00:04:52,738
<i>HAS PUSHED</i>
<i>THE "CHALLENGE" BUTTON.</i>

84
00:04:52,771 --> 00:04:54,738
-HUH?
-HUH?

85
00:04:54,771 --> 00:04:56,538
<i>-PLEASE PROCEED</i>
<i>DOWN THE HALL PROMPTLY.</i>

86
00:04:56,571 --> 00:04:58,338
-IF THERE WAS AN INTRUDER,

87
00:04:58,371 --> 00:05:00,505
YOU COULD HAVE EXECUTED HIM
ON THE SPOT.

88
00:05:00,538 --> 00:05:03,571
SO WHY USE YOUR PRIVILEGE
TO INCARCERATE HIM

89
00:05:03,605 --> 00:05:07,105
WITHOUT FIRST SEEKING
MY AUTHORIZATION?

90
00:05:07,138 --> 00:05:09,271
I WON'T GET ANGRY WITH YOU, LIZ.

91
00:05:09,305 --> 00:05:10,605
BUT THERE'S STILL

92
00:05:10,638 --> 00:05:13,271
SOMETHING YOU'RE HIDING FROM ME,
ISN'T THERE?

93
00:05:13,305 --> 00:05:14,438
-[ SIGHS ]

94
00:05:14,471 --> 00:05:16,405
BUT YOU'LL...BE MAD.

95
00:05:16,438 --> 00:05:17,405
-GO ON.

96
00:05:17,438 --> 00:05:19,238
-HEY, BOSS.

97
00:05:19,271 --> 00:05:20,705
CAN I TALK TO YOU ABOUT THAT
NEW PRISONER WE'VE GOT WHO --

98
00:05:20,738 --> 00:05:22,105
UH...

99
00:05:22,138 --> 00:05:23,505
OH. UH, SORRY.

100
00:05:23,538 --> 00:05:27,405
DID I COME AT A BAD TIME?
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

101
00:05:27,438 --> 00:05:30,371
-[ SIGHS ]
-A NEW PRISONER? DO TELL.

102
00:05:30,405 --> 00:05:33,171
-WAIT. ARE YOU SAYING
SHE HAS TO KILL STAZ?

103
00:05:33,205 --> 00:05:35,138
-THAT'S NOT WHAT I SAID.

104
00:05:35,171 --> 00:05:36,638
IF A GHOST HAS THE ABILITY

105
00:05:36,671 --> 00:05:39,371
TO COEXIST WITH MAGIC
OF OTHER SPECIES,

106
00:05:39,405 --> 00:05:41,505
THEN THEY CAN ESSENTIALLY
TURN INTO ANY DEMON

107
00:05:41,538 --> 00:05:43,038
BY CONSUMING THEM.

108
00:05:43,071 --> 00:05:45,471
CURRENTLY, THIS GIRL
HAS THE BODY OF A GHOST,

109
00:05:45,505 --> 00:05:48,738
BUT SHE ALSO HAS THE POTENTIAL
TO BECOME A VAMPIRE.

110
00:05:48,771 --> 00:05:50,505
AND IF THAT SHOULD EVER HAPPEN,

111
00:05:50,538 --> 00:05:53,305
IT WILL MEAN THE BIRTH
OF A MONSTROUS NEW HYBRID.

112
00:05:53,338 --> 00:05:54,738
-YOU'VE GONE WAY OVER THE LINE!

113
00:05:54,771 --> 00:05:57,171
WHAT'S THE POINT IN DOING THAT,
ANYWAY?

114
00:05:57,205 --> 00:05:59,738
STAZ WOULD STILL DIE FROM HAVING
ALL HIS MAGIC SUCKED OUT!

115
00:05:59,771 --> 00:06:02,438
-NO, HE'D CONTINUE TO LIVE
WITHIN THE GIRL'S BODY --

116
00:06:02,471 --> 00:06:03,671
-SHUT UP.

117
00:06:03,705 --> 00:06:05,271
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ANY MORE OF THIS.

118
00:06:05,305 --> 00:06:07,371
-BUT IT'S THE ONLY POSSIBLE WAY
WE CAN SAVE HER.

119
00:06:07,405 --> 00:06:09,005
IF LEFT ALONE,

120
00:06:09,038 --> 00:06:10,671
THE GIRL WILL COMPLETELY
DISAPPEAR FROM THIS WORLD.

121
00:06:12,338 --> 00:06:13,671
-THIS IS ALREADY THE 10th TIME

122
00:06:13,705 --> 00:06:15,671
THIS TURKEY'S CHALLENGED US
TO A FIGHT.

123
00:06:15,705 --> 00:06:17,271
-HE'S SUCH A PAIN IN THE ASS.

124
00:06:17,305 --> 00:06:19,105
CAN WE JUST KILL HIM ALREADY?

125
00:06:19,138 --> 00:06:21,605
-BROTHER, WAIT. I CAN EXPLAIN.

126
00:06:26,171 --> 00:06:27,271
[ GUNSHOTS ]

127
00:06:27,305 --> 00:06:28,571
-WHOA!

128
00:06:28,605 --> 00:06:30,405
-HE SHOT HIM RIGHT IN THE CHEST.
WAY TO GO!

129
00:06:32,271 --> 00:06:33,605
-[ GRUNTS ]

130
00:06:35,371 --> 00:06:36,438
[ GASPS ]

131
00:06:36,471 --> 00:06:37,505
BROTHER.

132
00:06:37,538 --> 00:06:39,171
-YOU'LL BE JUST FINE.

133
00:06:39,205 --> 00:06:42,338
THESE BULLETS WILL ALLOW
YOUR MAGIC TO RECOVER.

134
00:06:42,371 --> 00:06:44,505
-BY MAKING A HOLE IN MY CHEST?

135
00:06:44,538 --> 00:06:46,238
-DON'T WORRY.

136
00:06:46,271 --> 00:06:48,338
YOUR VAMPIRE BLOOD WILL HEAL
THOSE WOUNDS INSTANTLY.

137
00:06:48,371 --> 00:06:50,505
-WAIT. VAMPIRE BLOOD?

138
00:06:50,538 --> 00:06:52,638
AND WHAT'S ALL THIS STUFF
ABOUT "BROTHER"?

139
00:06:52,671 --> 00:06:54,205
-BOSS, IS THAT SCUMBA--

140
00:06:54,238 --> 00:06:56,438
I MEAN,
THAT GENTLEMAN YOUR BROTHER?

141
00:06:56,471 --> 00:06:58,438
-I HAVE MISSED YOU,
LITTLE BROTHER.

142
00:06:58,471 --> 00:07:02,005
-YEAH, WELL, I HOPE YOU DON'T
EXPECT ME TO SAY THE SAME.

143
00:07:02,038 --> 00:07:03,371
-THAT LOOKS LIKE...

144
00:07:03,405 --> 00:07:05,405
-YEAH, IT'S THE BOOK
OF HUMAN RESURRECTION.

145
00:07:05,438 --> 00:07:06,671
YOU WROTE IT, DIDN'T YOU?

146
00:07:06,705 --> 00:07:08,205
-YOU WANT MY AUTOGRAPH?

147
00:07:08,238 --> 00:07:09,571
-NO, DUMBASS.

148
00:07:09,605 --> 00:07:12,171
I WANT TO KNOW
WHAT THE STUPID THING SAYS.

149
00:07:12,205 --> 00:07:14,338
HOW TO BRING HUMANS
BACK TO LIFE --

150
00:07:14,371 --> 00:07:16,371
THAT'S WHAT I'VE COME
ALL THIS WAY TO FIND OUT.

151
00:07:16,405 --> 00:07:18,538
-IF WE DON'T
FIGURE SOMETHING OUT,

152
00:07:18,571 --> 00:07:20,371
SHE'S GONNA DISAPPEAR FOR GOOD!

153
00:07:20,405 --> 00:07:23,371
I DON'T WANT TO PICK
BETWEEN SAVING STAZ OR FUYUMI.

154
00:07:23,405 --> 00:07:24,705
-SO WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

155
00:07:24,738 --> 00:07:26,305
-WOW! WHAT'S UP, YOU GUYS?

156
00:07:26,338 --> 00:07:27,971
IT'S LIKE A FUNERAL IN HERE.

157
00:07:28,005 --> 00:07:29,505
[ TWINKLE! ]
TA-DA!

158
00:07:29,538 --> 00:07:31,205
I JUST COULDN'T STAND
HIDING FROM YOU GUYS ANYMORE!

159
00:07:31,238 --> 00:07:32,271
BELL'S IN THE HOUSE, YO!

160
00:07:32,305 --> 00:07:34,071
-BEAT IT, MARSHMALLOW!

161
00:07:34,105 --> 00:07:35,305
-YEAH, GET LOST, PUFFY!

162
00:07:35,338 --> 00:07:37,338
-I'M NOT A MARSHMALLOW
RIGHT NOW, GUYS!

163
00:07:37,371 --> 00:07:39,338
-WHAT DO YOU WANT, HYDRA?

164
00:07:39,371 --> 00:07:41,371
-LONG TIME NO SEE, FRANKEN.

165
00:07:41,405 --> 00:07:42,738
-YOU TWO KNOW EACH OTHER?

166
00:07:42,771 --> 00:07:44,371
-OF COURSE.

167
00:07:44,405 --> 00:07:46,338
IN FACT, FRANKEN IS ONE
OF MY REGULAR CLIENTS.

168
00:07:46,371 --> 00:07:48,738
BUT I'M NOT HERE
ON BUSINESS THIS TIME.

169
00:07:48,771 --> 00:07:52,371
I CAME 'CAUSE I HEARD WE'RE
ABOUT TO LOSE THIS NICE RACK.

170
00:07:52,405 --> 00:07:55,205
BUT, FRANKEN, YOU'RE NOT BEING
HONEST WITH THEM.

171
00:07:55,238 --> 00:07:57,371
THERE'S MORE THAN ONE WAY
TO SAVE FUYUMI.

172
00:07:57,405 --> 00:07:58,638
-WHICH IS...?

173
00:07:58,671 --> 00:08:00,971
AAH! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

174
00:08:01,005 --> 00:08:02,171
-IT'S LIKE THIS.

175
00:08:02,205 --> 00:08:04,371
YOU SEE,
I REALLY HATE BEING LIED TO.

176
00:08:04,405 --> 00:08:06,605
IF YOU DON'T WANT
TO GET KILLED RIGHT NOW,

177
00:08:06,638 --> 00:08:08,371
YOU'D BETTER START
TELLING THE TRUTH.

178
00:08:08,405 --> 00:08:10,138
-I REFUSE.

179
00:08:10,171 --> 00:08:13,271
SUPPOSE I DID TRY
TO TEACH YOU HOW IT'S DONE.

180
00:08:13,305 --> 00:08:15,205
WHAT WOULD I POSSIBLY
HAVE TO GAIN?

181
00:08:15,238 --> 00:08:16,405
-GIVE ME A BREAK.

182
00:08:16,438 --> 00:08:18,271
-WHY ARE YOU ASKING ME THIS?

183
00:08:18,305 --> 00:08:21,071
WHAT MANNER OF HUMAN
ARE YOU TRYING TO RESURRECT?

184
00:08:21,105 --> 00:08:22,305
A WOMAN?

185
00:08:22,338 --> 00:08:23,638
-THAT'S NONE
OF YOUR DAMN BUSINESS.

186
00:08:23,671 --> 00:08:26,038
-SO, IT <i>IS</i> A WOMAN.
A VIRGIN?

187
00:08:26,071 --> 00:08:27,538
-SHUT UP! YOU'RE SUCH A JERK!

188
00:08:27,571 --> 00:08:29,305
I SAID IT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS!

189
00:08:29,338 --> 00:08:31,205
IF I TOLD YOU,
WOULD IT CHANGE YOUR MIND?!

190
00:08:31,238 --> 00:08:33,038
-IT MIGHT MAKE
A DIFFERENCE, YES.

191
00:08:33,071 --> 00:08:34,338
-THAT'S A LIE!

192
00:08:34,371 --> 00:08:36,305
-[ LAUGHS ]

193
00:08:37,605 --> 00:08:38,971
-CHECK OUT LORD BRAZ.

194
00:08:39,005 --> 00:08:41,105
I'VE NEVER SEEN HIM
LAUGH LIKE THAT.

195
00:08:41,138 --> 00:08:43,038
-WELL, THEY ARE BROTHERS,
WORMBRAIN.

196
00:08:43,071 --> 00:08:44,071
THEY MUST GET ALONG.

197
00:08:44,105 --> 00:08:45,571
RIGHT, BOSS?

198
00:08:45,605 --> 00:08:47,538
-QUIET!

199
00:08:49,005 --> 00:08:50,705
-AW, CRAP! HOT, HOT, HOT!

200
00:08:50,738 --> 00:08:53,671
-I GUESS WE WEREN'T
SUPPOSED TO SAY THAT TO HER!

201
00:08:53,705 --> 00:08:56,205
SORRY!

202
00:08:56,238 --> 00:08:57,505
-WHAT'S WRONG, LIZ?

203
00:08:57,538 --> 00:08:59,271
WHY DID YOU BURN THE ZOMBIES
LIKE THAT?

204
00:08:59,305 --> 00:09:03,171
-STAZ COULDN'T DO THAT,
BUT I BEAT THE ZOMBIES EASILY.

205
00:09:03,205 --> 00:09:06,538
I REFUSE TO ACCEPT
THAT STAZ IS A NOBLE DEMON.

206
00:09:06,571 --> 00:09:08,971
HE'S TOO WEAK TO BE ONE OF US.

207
00:09:09,005 --> 00:09:10,571
-YOU'RE WRONG ABOUT THAT, LIZ.

208
00:09:10,605 --> 00:09:12,271
OUR BROTHER, STAZ,

209
00:09:12,305 --> 00:09:15,138
IS BOTH A NOBLE DEMON
AND A PURE-BLOODED VAMPIRE.

210
00:09:15,171 --> 00:09:17,138
NOTHING WILL EVER ALTER THAT.

211
00:09:17,171 --> 00:09:19,538
AND HE WILL ALWAYS
BE YOUR OLDER BROTHER.

212
00:09:19,571 --> 00:09:20,671
-NO!

213
00:09:20,705 --> 00:09:22,571
I'M THE ONE WHO'S USEFUL TO YOU,

214
00:09:22,605 --> 00:09:23,638
NOT HIM!

215
00:09:27,538 --> 00:09:31,171
I'M BETTER THAN HIM
IN EVERY WAY.

216
00:09:31,205 --> 00:09:34,571
-I'M SORRY, LITTLE SISTER,
BUT YOU'RE MISTAKEN.

217
00:09:34,605 --> 00:09:37,438
-WHY ARE YOU ALWAYS LIKE THAT,
BROTHER?

218
00:09:39,938 --> 00:09:41,405
[ Voice breaking ]
YOU'VE ALWAYS DONE IT --

219
00:09:41,438 --> 00:09:44,271
TREATED HIM
SO MUCH BETTER THAN ME.

220
00:09:47,271 --> 00:09:48,571
WHEN YOU RAN AWAY BEFORE,

221
00:09:48,605 --> 00:09:51,138
I HAD HOPED THAT BROTHER
WOULD FINALLY START

222
00:09:51,171 --> 00:09:52,571
PAYING MORE ATTENTION TO ME.

223
00:09:52,605 --> 00:09:55,205
INSTEAD, HE'D SPEND TIME

224
00:09:55,238 --> 00:09:57,538
LOOKING THROUGH
YOUR OLD PHOTO ALBUMS

225
00:09:57,571 --> 00:09:59,238
OR CHECKING UP ON YOU

226
00:09:59,271 --> 00:10:02,138
THROUGH SOME MAIL-ORDER
CRYSTAL BALL.

227
00:10:02,171 --> 00:10:04,171
HE DIDN'T COME TO SEE <i>ME</i> TODAY!

228
00:10:04,205 --> 00:10:06,038
HE ONLY CAME TO SEE YOU, STAZ!

229
00:10:06,071 --> 00:10:07,471
-THAT'S NOT TRUE, LIZ.

230
00:10:07,505 --> 00:10:08,571
I <i>DO</i> CARE.

231
00:10:08,605 --> 00:10:10,205
-STOP LYING TO ME.

232
00:10:10,238 --> 00:10:11,971
WHEN YOU WALKED IN,
YOU COULDN'T EVEN REMEMBER

233
00:10:12,005 --> 00:10:13,271
THAT I DON'T LIKE COFFEE!

234
00:10:13,305 --> 00:10:15,505
-BUT I ALREADY APOLOGIZED
TO YOU.

235
00:10:15,538 --> 00:10:17,371
-YOU HAVEN'T CHANGED A BIT, HUH?

236
00:10:17,405 --> 00:10:18,938
YOU USED YOUR AUTHORITY

237
00:10:18,971 --> 00:10:21,271
TO THROW ME IN HERE
FOR A REASON LIKE THAT?

238
00:10:21,305 --> 00:10:22,571
-I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

239
00:10:22,605 --> 00:10:24,305
YOU COULD NEVER UNDERSTAND
HOW I FEEL.

240
00:10:24,338 --> 00:10:26,638
-AND YOU COULDN'T UNDERSTAND
THE WAY I FEEL, EITHER.

241
00:10:26,671 --> 00:10:28,338
SO, I GUESS WE'RE EVEN, THEN.

242
00:10:28,371 --> 00:10:30,405
WE'RE BOTH DOING THINGS
FOR STUPID REASONS.

243
00:10:30,438 --> 00:10:32,905
YOU'RE DOING THIS
FOR OUR BROTHER

244
00:10:32,938 --> 00:10:35,171
WHILE I HAVE MY OWN REASONS
TO BE DESPERATE.

245
00:10:35,205 --> 00:10:36,938
AND GUESS WHAT?

246
00:10:36,971 --> 00:10:38,238
THE ANSWER
TO BOTH OF OUR PROBLEMS

247
00:10:38,271 --> 00:10:40,405
IS THE GUY SITTING
RIGHT NEXT TO YOU.

248
00:10:40,438 --> 00:10:42,405
-YOU'VE BECOME
QUITE THE SMOOTH TALKER.

249
00:10:42,438 --> 00:10:44,105
FINE.
-[ SNIFFLES ]

250
00:10:44,138 --> 00:10:47,105
-IF YOU DO A FAVOR FOR ME,
THEN I'LL TELL YOU

251
00:10:47,138 --> 00:10:50,071
EVERYTHING THERE IS TO KNOW
ABOUT RESURRECTING HUMANS.

252
00:10:51,538 --> 00:10:53,238
-SORRY. I COULDN'T HEAR YOU.

253
00:10:53,271 --> 00:10:55,505
-I SAID THERE'S ANOTHER WAY.

254
00:10:55,538 --> 00:10:59,005
-INSTEAD OF TAKING OVER
THE VAMPIRE, YOU REMOVE IT.

255
00:10:59,038 --> 00:11:01,271
-IN OTHER WORDS, TURN HER
BACK INTO A PLAIN GHOST.

256
00:11:01,305 --> 00:11:02,305
IS THAT IT?

257
00:11:02,338 --> 00:11:03,571
-IF THAT'S POSSIBLE,

258
00:11:03,605 --> 00:11:06,038
WHY DID YOU KEEP QUIET
ALL THIS TIME?

259
00:11:06,071 --> 00:11:07,571
OUR PROBLEM
WOULD HAVE BEEN SOLVED

260
00:11:07,605 --> 00:11:09,338
IF YOU HAD JUST SAID THAT

261
00:11:09,371 --> 00:11:11,305
INSTEAD OF ALL THIS CRAZY TALK
ABOUT CREATING HYBRIDS!

262
00:11:11,338 --> 00:11:15,471
-THAT MAY BE TRUE FOR YOU,
BUT CERTAINLY NOT FOR ME.

263
00:11:15,505 --> 00:11:18,305
THE SITUATION
IS RAPIDLY DETERIORATING.

264
00:11:18,338 --> 00:11:19,538
-HUH?

265
00:11:19,571 --> 00:11:21,471
-I CAN'T AFFORD TO WASTE
ANY MORE TIME.

266
00:11:21,505 --> 00:11:24,105
I CREATED SOMETHING
THAT'S HORRENDOUS,

267
00:11:24,138 --> 00:11:25,338
A TRUE ABOMINATION.

268
00:11:25,371 --> 00:11:27,171
IF I AM UNABLE TO STOP HIM...

269
00:11:27,205 --> 00:11:28,438
-HIS EXISTENCE COULD MEAN

270
00:11:28,471 --> 00:11:30,838
THE EXTINCTION
OF THE ENTIRE DEMON RACE,

271
00:11:30,871 --> 00:11:32,471
DESTROYING DEMON WORLD.

272
00:11:32,505 --> 00:11:33,938
-WHAT?

273
00:11:33,971 --> 00:11:36,138
THE EXTINCTION
OF THE DEMON RACE?

274
00:11:36,171 --> 00:11:37,605
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

275
00:11:37,638 --> 00:11:39,338
-JUST THREE DAYS AGO,

276
00:11:39,371 --> 00:11:42,305
IN AN AREA OF DEMON WORLD
THAT I'VE BEEN WATCHING OVER,

277
00:11:42,338 --> 00:11:45,105
HE FIRST APPEARED
AND MADE HIS PRESENCE KNOWN.

278
00:11:45,138 --> 00:11:46,271
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

279
00:11:46,305 --> 00:11:49,205
-ARTIFICIAL DEMON NUMBER 9.

280
00:11:49,238 --> 00:11:52,171
AKIM PAPRADON.

281
00:11:55,146 --> 00:11:57,512
THAT DEMON WAS, WITHOUT A DOUBT,

282
00:11:57,546 --> 00:12:00,112
THE GREATEST MASTERPIECE
I'VE EVER CREATED.

283
00:12:00,146 --> 00:12:01,112
-ARTIFICIAL...

284
00:12:01,146 --> 00:12:02,279
-DEMON?

285
00:12:02,312 --> 00:12:04,312
MY ANCESTOR
ONCE STITCHED TOGETHER

286
00:12:04,346 --> 00:12:06,279
DIFFERENT PIECES
OF HUMAN CORPSES

287
00:12:06,312 --> 00:12:08,179
IN ORDER TO CREATE A MONSTER.

288
00:12:08,212 --> 00:12:10,279
AND I STITCHED TOGETHER
PIECES OF DEMONS

289
00:12:10,312 --> 00:12:13,112
TO TRY TO CREATE
AN EVEN GREATER MONSTER.

290
00:12:13,146 --> 00:12:16,979
AT LEAST, THAT WAS THE IDEA.

291
00:12:17,012 --> 00:12:18,379
-NO.

292
00:12:18,412 --> 00:12:20,279
THIS ISN'T GOOD ENOUGH.

293
00:12:20,312 --> 00:12:22,979
THIS WON'T DO AT ALL, FRANKEN.

294
00:12:23,012 --> 00:12:25,046
I NEED HIGHER-QUALITY PARTS

295
00:12:25,079 --> 00:12:27,346
THAT ARE WORTHY
OF THIS BODY YOU MADE FOR ME.

296
00:12:27,379 --> 00:12:29,112
-BUT THAT'S MUCH TOO DANGEROUS.

297
00:12:29,146 --> 00:12:31,746
WE NEED TO USE PARTS
THAT YOU CAN STILL CONTROL.

298
00:12:31,779 --> 00:12:33,246
-ENOUGH OF YOUR EXCUSES.

299
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:34,912
-BESIDES,
WHERE WOULD I COME UP WITH --

300
00:12:34,946 --> 00:12:36,012
-ENOUGH!

301
00:12:36,046 --> 00:12:38,879
I'LL GO FIND THEM MYSELF.

302
00:12:38,912 --> 00:12:40,279
-SPATIAL MAGIC?

303
00:12:40,312 --> 00:12:42,479
-I WAS SURPRISED, AS WELL.

304
00:12:42,512 --> 00:12:45,512
I WASN'T AWARE HE HAD
SUCH INCREDIBLE POWERS,

305
00:12:45,546 --> 00:12:49,146
AND I ALLOWED HIM TO ESCAPE
IN AN INCOMPLETE STATE.

306
00:12:49,179 --> 00:12:51,312
-THEN ALL THAT CRAP
ABOUT CREATING HYBRIDS

307
00:12:51,346 --> 00:12:53,246
WAS JUST SO YOU COULD STOP HIM.

308
00:12:53,279 --> 00:12:56,479
MAN, YOU REALLY
DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

309
00:12:56,512 --> 00:12:58,279
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

310
00:12:58,312 --> 00:13:00,412
-I'M THE BOSS OF THIS AREA NOW.

311
00:13:00,446 --> 00:13:03,012
AND WHENEVER THERE'S TROUBLE
IN MY TERRITORY,

312
00:13:03,046 --> 00:13:06,212
I SQUASH IT LIKE A BUG
BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT I DO.

313
00:13:06,246 --> 00:13:07,846
-DON'T BE CRAZY!

314
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:09,312
YOU HAVEN'T ANY IDEA HOW --

315
00:13:09,346 --> 00:13:11,346
-STRONG HE IS?
THAT'S PERFECT.

316
00:13:11,379 --> 00:13:14,246
BECAUSE I'VE BEEN LOOKING
ALL OVER FOR A GUY LIKE THAT.

317
00:13:14,279 --> 00:13:15,779
ALL RIGHT, HERE'S THE DEAL.

318
00:13:15,812 --> 00:13:18,412
YOU FIX FUYUMI.

319
00:13:18,446 --> 00:13:20,312
-[ SIGHS ] VERY WELL.

320
00:13:20,346 --> 00:13:21,779
PROVIDED, OF COURSE,

321
00:13:21,812 --> 00:13:24,012
THAT YOU'RE ABLE
TO STOP HIM FIRST.

322
00:13:24,046 --> 00:13:27,179
-HEY! COME ON!
YOU GOT TO START ON HER NOW!

323
00:13:27,212 --> 00:13:29,246
IF WE WASTE MORE TIME,
SHE'LL DISAPPEAR!

324
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,512
-NO.

325
00:13:30,546 --> 00:13:32,312
I'M ABLE TO SUSTAIN
THE GIRL'S BODY

326
00:13:32,346 --> 00:13:33,846
FOR HALF A DAY.

327
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:36,979
STOP HIM BEFORE THAT.
THEN I'LL FIX HER.

328
00:13:37,012 --> 00:13:39,712
SO THAT'S THE DEAL,
AND YOU CAN TAKE IT OR LEAVE IT.

329
00:13:39,746 --> 00:13:40,979
YOUR CHOICE.

330
00:13:41,012 --> 00:13:44,279
-SO...
WHERE IS THAT STINKIN' HYBRID?

331
00:13:44,312 --> 00:13:46,146
-[ PANTING ] AAH!

332
00:13:47,912 --> 00:13:49,179
AAH!

333
00:13:49,212 --> 00:13:50,846
W-WHAT ARE YOU?!

334
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,146
WHY HAVE
YOU BEEN FOLLOWING ME?!

335
00:13:52,179 --> 00:13:53,179
WHY?!

336
00:13:53,212 --> 00:13:55,946
-YOU'VE GOT FAST LEGS.

337
00:13:55,979 --> 00:13:57,946
WHAT DO YOU SAY? WANT TO TRADE?

338
00:13:57,979 --> 00:13:59,212
-AAH!

339
00:13:59,246 --> 00:14:01,012
AAH!

340
00:14:01,046 --> 00:14:03,412
-THEN HE APPEARED IN THE NORTH.

341
00:14:03,446 --> 00:14:05,979
HE'S SEEKING OUT
NEW PARTS FOR HIS BODY,

342
00:14:06,012 --> 00:14:09,412
WANDERING, PLUNDERING,
AND EVOLVING.

343
00:14:09,446 --> 00:14:11,979
-DOESN'T SOUND VERY GOOD.
-NOT AT ALL.

344
00:14:12,012 --> 00:14:14,312
AND SOMETHING NEEDS TO BE DONE
IMMEDIATELY.

345
00:14:14,346 --> 00:14:17,012
-SO WHAT IS IT THAT
YOU WANT ME TO DO EXACTLY?

346
00:14:17,046 --> 00:14:19,146
-I WON'T ASK FOR THE IMPOSSIBLE.

347
00:14:19,179 --> 00:14:20,979
AND, FRANKLY,
THE SHAPE YOU'RE IN NOW,

348
00:14:21,012 --> 00:14:23,112
I DON'T THINK THAT YOU <i>CAN</i> DO
MUCH AGAINST HIM.

349
00:14:23,146 --> 00:14:24,846
-YOU'RE RIGHT. I CAN'T.

350
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,746
NOW, IF YOU WANTED ME
TO SNAP A FEW PICTURES OF HIM,

351
00:14:26,779 --> 00:14:28,212
I COULD DO THAT, BUT...

352
00:14:28,246 --> 00:14:31,712
-WHAT IF YOU WERE TO REGAIN
YOUR FORMER POWERS?

353
00:14:31,746 --> 00:14:33,179
-WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

354
00:14:33,212 --> 00:14:36,012
-THE BULLET I FIRED INSIDE YOU
LONG AGO.

355
00:14:36,046 --> 00:14:37,679
IT'S STILL RIGHT HERE, ISN'T IT?

356
00:14:37,712 --> 00:14:39,946
SURELY YOU HAVEN'T FORGOTTEN.

357
00:14:41,479 --> 00:14:42,879
-YEAH.

358
00:14:42,912 --> 00:14:44,179
I REMEMBER.

359
00:14:44,212 --> 00:14:46,379
AND HOW YOU TRIED
TO KILL YOUR OWN BROTHER.

360
00:14:47,846 --> 00:14:48,912
[ BONES CRACK ]

361
00:14:48,946 --> 00:14:50,746
-IS THAT REALLY WHAT YOU THOUGHT

362
00:14:50,779 --> 00:14:52,212
MY TRUE OBJECTIVE WAS?

363
00:14:52,246 --> 00:14:53,879
DO YOU RECOGNIZE THIS?

364
00:14:53,912 --> 00:14:55,379
-THAT OLD MAGIC TRICK?

365
00:14:55,412 --> 00:14:57,712
-NO, I'M REFERRING
TO THE OBJECT.

366
00:14:57,746 --> 00:14:58,979
-NOT REALLY.

367
00:14:59,012 --> 00:15:01,046
HEY, DIDN'T I BREAK YOUR WRIST
JUST NOW?

368
00:15:01,079 --> 00:15:03,712
'CAUSE, YOU'RE KIND OF ACTING
LIKE IT NEVER EVEN HAPPENED.

369
00:15:03,746 --> 00:15:06,146
-I MERELY LET YOU THINK
THAT YOU HAD BROKEN IT.

370
00:15:06,179 --> 00:15:08,012
AT THE MOMENT,
YOU'RE SIMPLY TOO WEAK

371
00:15:08,046 --> 00:15:09,812
TO ASCERTAIN THE DIFFERENCE.

372
00:15:09,846 --> 00:15:11,312
BUT THIS IS YOUR TRUE POWER.

373
00:15:11,346 --> 00:15:12,712
YOU MADE THIS.

374
00:15:12,746 --> 00:15:15,212
IT WAS A BOULDER
FIVE METERS ACROSS.

375
00:15:15,246 --> 00:15:17,112
-WHAT?

376
00:15:17,146 --> 00:15:19,946
-[ Thinking ] <i>THIS TASTE.</i>

377
00:15:19,979 --> 00:15:23,112
THIS IS WHAT I WAS CRAVING FOR.

378
00:15:23,146 --> 00:15:27,079
-LOOK! SHE'S DRINKING IT!
IS THIS THAT EMERGENCY STUFF?

379
00:15:27,112 --> 00:15:30,079
<i>-BUT IT TASTES</i>
<i>A LITTLE DIFFERENT TO ME.</i>

380
00:15:30,112 --> 00:15:31,946
<i>THIS ISN'T STAZ'S BLOOD.</i>

381
00:15:31,979 --> 00:15:35,812
-YES, IT'S A CONCENTRATED
MAGICAL ESSENCE FORMULA.

382
00:15:35,846 --> 00:15:37,079
-WHO ARE --

383
00:15:37,112 --> 00:15:38,112
-ARE YOU AWAKE?

384
00:15:38,146 --> 00:15:40,879
-[ GASPS, SCREAMS SOFTLY ]

385
00:15:40,912 --> 00:15:43,012
-WHAT A TINY SCREAM.
-OH!

386
00:15:43,046 --> 00:15:44,112
-HEY, YOU OKAY?

387
00:15:44,146 --> 00:15:45,179
-WHAT HAPPENED?

388
00:15:45,212 --> 00:15:46,812
WAIT. WHERE DID WOLF GO?

389
00:15:46,846 --> 00:15:48,146
I THOUGHT HE WAS HERE.

390
00:15:48,179 --> 00:15:49,879
-AFRAID HE HAD TO STEP OUT.

391
00:15:49,912 --> 00:15:51,179
TO KILL A MO--

392
00:15:51,212 --> 00:15:53,746
I MEAN,
TO KEEP YOU FROM DISAPPEARING.

393
00:15:55,779 --> 00:15:57,412
-SO, ARE YOU READY?
-YEAH.

394
00:15:57,446 --> 00:15:59,812
-YOU MEAN, YOU HAD TO COME BACK
HERE AND CHANGE YOUR CLOTHES

395
00:15:59,846 --> 00:16:01,312
JUST SO YOU COULD
GO KICK SOME ASS?

396
00:16:01,346 --> 00:16:02,979
-THAT'S NOT WHY I'M HERE.

397
00:16:03,012 --> 00:16:04,246
I CAME TO GET THIS.

398
00:16:04,279 --> 00:16:05,346
-A POLE?

399
00:16:05,379 --> 00:16:07,079
-[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

400
00:16:09,346 --> 00:16:11,279
ALL RIGHT.
-WHAT WAS THAT?

401
00:16:11,312 --> 00:16:13,812
-I JUST SEALED MY MAGIC
INSIDE OF THIS.

402
00:16:13,846 --> 00:16:16,879
NOW IT'S LIKE AN EXTENSION
OF MY OWN BODY.

403
00:16:16,912 --> 00:16:18,812
-YEAH, I STILL DON'T GET IT.

404
00:16:18,846 --> 00:16:21,679
-TRUST ME.
YOU'RE ABOUT TO FIND OUT.

405
00:16:21,712 --> 00:16:23,346
THAT THING'S GONNA FEEL
MY POWDER!

406
00:16:23,379 --> 00:16:24,846
-THAT'S <i>POWER.</i>

407
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:26,346
-FOR BEAUTIFUL HUMAN LIFE.

408
00:16:26,379 --> 00:16:28,179
-[ Flatly ]
I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE IT.

409
00:16:28,212 --> 00:16:29,179
-UH, YEAH.

410
00:16:29,212 --> 00:16:30,346
-BETTER GET GOING.

411
00:16:30,379 --> 00:16:33,879
THE NEXT STOP --
NORTH DEMON WORLD.

412
00:16:35,412 --> 00:16:37,346
-HOW MUCH TIME DO I HAVE?

413
00:16:37,379 --> 00:16:40,846
-AS MUCH TIME AS IT TAKES
FOR THIS FORMULA TO RUN OUT.

414
00:16:40,879 --> 00:16:42,912
SHE'LL NEED TO DRINK IT
ONCE EVERY HOUR.

415
00:16:42,946 --> 00:16:44,712
THAT WILL LAST HER HALF A DAY.

416
00:16:44,746 --> 00:16:46,346
-THAT SOUNDS KIND OF FISHY.

417
00:16:46,379 --> 00:16:47,812
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE

418
00:16:47,846 --> 00:16:49,212
YOU WERE GONNA TRY
TO CREATE A HYBRID

419
00:16:49,246 --> 00:16:50,612
WITH ONLY THAT MUCH STUFF.

420
00:16:50,646 --> 00:16:52,379
-DON'T GET THE WRONG IDEA.

421
00:16:52,412 --> 00:16:56,746
IN TERMS OF MY MAGICAL FORMULAS,
I HAVE AN EXTENSIVE ASSORTMENT,

422
00:16:56,779 --> 00:16:58,979
ENOUGH TO LAST HER FOR A WEEK,

423
00:16:59,012 --> 00:17:01,146
BUT IF I WANT
TO KEEP HER A GHOST

424
00:17:01,179 --> 00:17:03,112
WITHOUT MIXING IN ANYTHING ELSE,

425
00:17:03,146 --> 00:17:05,612
THEN I CAN ONLY USE
SOME OF THE DRINKS HERE.

426
00:17:05,646 --> 00:17:08,012
-[ GRUMBLES ]

427
00:17:08,046 --> 00:17:10,912
-SO HURRY.
YOU HAVE LESS THAN ONE DAY.

428
00:17:10,946 --> 00:17:12,612
-AAH!

429
00:17:12,646 --> 00:17:14,912
-NOW, THEN. LEND ME A HAND.

430
00:17:14,946 --> 00:17:17,312
YOU TAKE MINE,
AND I'LL TAKE YOURS.

431
00:17:17,346 --> 00:17:18,946
-AAHHHH!

432
00:17:18,979 --> 00:17:20,346
-CAN I SEE?

433
00:17:20,379 --> 00:17:22,279
-DON'T LOSE IT NOW, OKAY?

434
00:17:22,312 --> 00:17:25,046
-W-WAIT. I, UH -- WHAT?

435
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:28,646
-DO YOU RECALL MY ATTEMPTS
TO UNLOCK YOUR TRUE POTENTIAL?

436
00:17:28,679 --> 00:17:30,946
WELL, I FINALLY SUCCEEDED.

437
00:17:30,979 --> 00:17:34,179
BUT AT THE SAME TIME,
IT WAS A FAILURE.

438
00:17:34,212 --> 00:17:37,046
[ THUNDER CRACKS ]

439
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:41,146
WELL, STAZ, WHAT DID YOU WANT
TO SHOW ME?

440
00:17:41,179 --> 00:17:43,212
-OH. BROTHER, WATCH THIS.

441
00:17:44,679 --> 00:17:46,312
[ CHUCKLES ]

442
00:17:52,346 --> 00:17:54,312
DID YOU SEE THAT?
IT'S NEAT, HUH?

443
00:17:54,346 --> 00:17:55,879
-Y-YES.

444
00:17:55,912 --> 00:17:57,846
-YOU CAN HAVE IT.

445
00:17:57,879 --> 00:17:59,112
-STAZ, WAIT.

446
00:17:59,146 --> 00:18:00,779
YOUR NOSE IS BLEEDING.

447
00:18:00,812 --> 00:18:03,012
WHERE ARE YOU GOING? STAZ!

448
00:18:03,046 --> 00:18:04,912
-NEXT, I COULD --

449
00:18:04,946 --> 00:18:06,212
HUH?

450
00:18:12,112 --> 00:18:13,712
-YOU ALWAYS COLLAPSED

451
00:18:13,746 --> 00:18:16,712
IMMEDIATELY AFTER USING
YOUR TRUE POWERS.

452
00:18:16,746 --> 00:18:19,079
BUT, IT DIDN'T SEEM AS THOUGH
YOU USED THEM BY CHOICE

453
00:18:19,112 --> 00:18:21,279
IT WAS AS THOUGH
AN INCREDIBLE ENERGY

454
00:18:21,312 --> 00:18:24,046
OVERFLOWED FROM A TINY VESSEL.

455
00:18:25,212 --> 00:18:27,179
-HUH?

456
00:18:27,212 --> 00:18:28,946
-IF THIS CONTINUED,
YOU WOULD HAVE SURELY DIED.

457
00:18:28,979 --> 00:18:30,612
IT WAS FAULT

458
00:18:30,646 --> 00:18:33,146
FOR TRYING TO UNLOCK YOUR POWER
SO PREMATURELY.

459
00:18:33,179 --> 00:18:34,779
-B-BROTHER.

460
00:18:34,812 --> 00:18:35,979
[ GUNSHOT ]

461
00:18:36,012 --> 00:18:37,279
-AND AS A RESULT,

462
00:18:37,312 --> 00:18:39,912
I DECIDED
TO RESTRAIN YOUR POWERS.

463
00:18:39,946 --> 00:18:41,879
THAT'S THE TRUE STORY.

464
00:18:41,912 --> 00:18:44,712
NOW, THREE DAYS
AFTER THAT MONSTER APPEARED,

465
00:18:44,746 --> 00:18:46,079
YOU SHOW UP,

466
00:18:46,112 --> 00:18:48,746
FULLY GROWN INTO A VESSEL
SUITABLE FOR THAT POWER.

467
00:18:48,779 --> 00:18:51,079
I SENSE DESTINY AT WORK.

468
00:18:51,112 --> 00:18:52,246
THE TIME HAS COME.

469
00:18:52,279 --> 00:18:54,746
I WILL REMOVE THE BULLET
FROM YOUR HEART.

470
00:18:54,779 --> 00:18:58,146
THEN YOU CAN SHOW ME
ALL YOUR POWER --

471
00:18:58,179 --> 00:19:00,946
THE FULL VAMPIRE POWER
INSIDE OF YOU.

472
00:19:00,979 --> 00:19:03,646
-THANKS.
I THINK I'M COOL THE WAY I AM.

473
00:19:03,679 --> 00:19:05,646
-UH...

474
00:19:05,679 --> 00:19:06,646
WAIT. WHAT?

475
00:19:06,679 --> 00:19:07,879
-IF YOU TAKE THE BULLET OUT,

476
00:19:07,912 --> 00:19:09,612
THEN I'M JUST GONNA
HAVE TO FIGHT

477
00:19:09,646 --> 00:19:10,979
WITH THAT BIG MONSTER, RIGHT?

478
00:19:11,012 --> 00:19:12,246
FORGET IT.

479
00:19:12,279 --> 00:19:13,646
THAT'S WAY TOO MUCH
RESPONSIBILITY.

480
00:19:13,679 --> 00:19:15,179
LEARNING
ABOUT HUMAN RESURRECTION

481
00:19:15,212 --> 00:19:16,712
IS ENOUGH FOR ME.

482
00:19:16,746 --> 00:19:18,812
I DON'T WANT YOU ADDING IN
EXTRA BONUSES

483
00:19:18,846 --> 00:19:20,812
AND CHANGING AROUND
THE TERMS OF OUR DEAL.

484
00:19:20,846 --> 00:19:22,279
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN BONUSES?

485
00:19:22,312 --> 00:19:23,879
YOU'D HAVE YOUR POWERS BACK!

486
00:19:23,912 --> 00:19:25,879
-THAT'S OKAY.
I'M FINE WITHOUT THEM.

487
00:19:25,912 --> 00:19:28,279
SO FORGET ABOUT THAT,
AND LET'S WRAP UP THIS DEAL.

488
00:19:28,312 --> 00:19:29,646
-I SEE.

489
00:19:29,679 --> 00:19:30,646
LIZ!

490
00:19:30,679 --> 00:19:31,779
-YES?!

491
00:19:31,812 --> 00:19:33,046
OH. [ WHIMPERS ]

492
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:35,246
[ ZING! ]
[ WHIMPERS ]

493
00:19:35,279 --> 00:19:36,846
-BRING OUT THE ZOMBIES.

494
00:19:36,879 --> 00:19:38,079
-HUH?

495
00:19:38,112 --> 00:19:39,579
-DID YOU HEAR ME?

496
00:19:39,612 --> 00:19:41,546
-[ SHOUTS ]

497
00:19:41,579 --> 00:19:43,079
-HEY. WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

498
00:19:43,112 --> 00:19:44,879
-OUR NEGOTIATIONS ARE OFF.

499
00:19:44,912 --> 00:19:47,112
SO, FROM HERE ON,
THERE WILL BE NO MORE DEALS.

500
00:19:48,712 --> 00:19:50,579
-[ GRUNTS ]
-[ CHUCKLES ]

501
00:19:50,612 --> 00:19:51,879
-THIS IS AN ORDER.

502
00:19:51,912 --> 00:19:53,579
KILL MY BROTHER.

503
00:19:53,612 --> 00:19:54,979
-HUH?
-YOU SURE?

504
00:19:55,012 --> 00:19:55,946
-UH...

505
00:19:55,979 --> 00:19:57,079
-ROGER!
-ROGER!

506
00:19:57,112 --> 00:19:58,612
-WHAT WILL IT BE?

507
00:19:58,646 --> 00:20:00,079
YOU'LL DIE
UNLESS THE BULLET IS REMOVED.

508
00:20:00,112 --> 00:20:02,579
-[ GROWLS ] DAMN YOU!

509
00:20:04,846 --> 00:20:06,179
-OKAY, WE GOT A BLOODY WALL

510
00:20:06,212 --> 00:20:08,646
AND NO SIGN OF THIS GUY
WE'RE LOOKING FOR.

511
00:20:08,679 --> 00:20:10,112
HOW WILL YOU FIND HIM?

512
00:20:10,146 --> 00:20:12,512
-BY CHALLENGING
THE TERRITORY BOSS.

513
00:20:12,546 --> 00:20:13,779
-YOU'RE WOLF OF THE WEST?

514
00:20:13,812 --> 00:20:15,846
-THIS LITTLE PUNK?
YOU'RE KIDDING ME!

515
00:20:15,879 --> 00:20:18,912
-YOU CAME ALL THE WAY HERE
TO TAKE OVER, HUH?

516
00:20:18,946 --> 00:20:20,746
-WELL, AIN'T THAT NICE.

517
00:20:20,779 --> 00:20:21,912
-BOSS.

518
00:20:21,946 --> 00:20:24,212
AW, DAMN.
IT'S JUST A LITTLE KID.

519
00:20:24,246 --> 00:20:27,112
THOUGHT IT'D BE THAT MONSTER
I'VE BEEN HEARING SO MUCH ABOUT.

520
00:20:27,146 --> 00:20:28,546
-THAT MAKES SENSE.

521
00:20:28,579 --> 00:20:29,879
I GUESS
THIS IS PROBABLY THE PLACE

522
00:20:29,912 --> 00:20:31,812
YOU FIGURED
HE'D BE COMING NEXT, RIGHT?

523
00:20:31,846 --> 00:20:34,012
-HOLD ON.
SO YOU KNOW ABOUT HIM, TOO?

524
00:20:34,046 --> 00:20:37,112
-BUT SINCE THE BOSS IS ALIVE,
MAYBE IT PASSED ON BY.

525
00:20:37,146 --> 00:20:39,246
AFTER ALL,
THE BOSS IS A WEAK-LOOKING PIG.

526
00:20:39,279 --> 00:20:40,512
-HUH?

527
00:20:40,546 --> 00:20:41,979
YOU LITTLE WEAKLING!

528
00:20:42,012 --> 00:20:43,112
I'M NOT A PIG!

529
00:20:43,146 --> 00:20:45,779
AAHHH!

530
00:20:45,812 --> 00:20:47,679
-UH-OH!
-MOVE IT!

531
00:20:47,712 --> 00:20:50,279
-[ SNORTS ]

532
00:20:50,312 --> 00:20:51,779
-YEAH, YOU ARE.

533
00:20:51,812 --> 00:20:53,179
-I'M NOT A PIG!

534
00:20:53,212 --> 00:20:54,546
I'M A BOAR!

535
00:20:54,579 --> 00:20:56,046
-OINK, OINK, PIGGY.

536
00:21:00,512 --> 00:21:01,812
SORRY.

537
00:21:01,846 --> 00:21:03,512
GOT TO BORROW YOUR TERRITORY.

538
00:21:03,546 --> 00:21:04,612
I'M THE BOSS NOW.

539
00:21:04,646 --> 00:21:06,712
-[ SNORTING ]

540
00:21:06,746 --> 00:21:08,246
YOU LITTLE TWERP.

541
00:21:08,279 --> 00:21:09,812
DON'T YOU GET COCKY!

542
00:21:09,846 --> 00:21:11,046
-RELAX.

543
00:21:11,079 --> 00:21:12,612
IT'S NOT LIKE
I WANT TO KILL YOU.

544
00:21:12,646 --> 00:21:14,879
-TOO BAD. 'CAUSE I DO!

545
00:21:18,846 --> 00:21:20,712
M-MY BODY!

546
00:21:20,746 --> 00:21:23,479
WHAT'S HAPPENING TO ME?

547
00:21:23,512 --> 00:21:25,879
H-HELP ME!

548
00:21:28,612 --> 00:21:30,246
-[ CHUCKLES ]

549
00:21:34,612 --> 00:21:35,946
HI.

550
00:21:37,212 --> 00:21:38,779
-[ LAUGHS ]

551
00:21:38,812 --> 00:21:40,046
-[ GRUNTS, GAGS ]

552
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:41,712
-AAH!

553
00:21:42,812 --> 00:21:43,812
-YOU JERK!

554
00:21:43,846 --> 00:21:45,579
THIS IS BLACKMAIL!

555
00:21:46,646 --> 00:21:48,179
-SORRY.

556
00:21:48,212 --> 00:21:51,612
I'M AFRAID A REFUSAL IS
NO LONGER ONE OF YOUR OPTIONS,

557
00:21:51,646 --> 00:21:54,712
AND A NEGOTIATION
IS OUT OF THE QUESTION.

558
00:21:54,746 --> 00:21:58,612
YOU SEE, WE WERE NEVER
TRULY ON EQUAL FOOTING.

559
00:21:58,646 --> 00:22:00,112
THAT IS...

560
00:22:02,012 --> 00:22:03,946
...UNTIL THIS MOMENT.

561
00:22:03,979 --> 00:22:05,212
-[ GRUNTS ]

562
00:22:07,812 --> 00:22:09,679
-DID YOU JUST KILL HIM FOR REAL?

563
00:22:09,712 --> 00:22:11,046
-WHAT A LETDOWN.

564
00:22:13,012 --> 00:22:15,846
[ HEART BEATING ]

565
00:22:15,879 --> 00:22:18,446
-NO, HE'S STILL ALIVE FOR NOW.

566
00:22:18,479 --> 00:22:20,679
DO WHATEVER YOU WANT WITH HIM.

567
00:22:20,712 --> 00:22:23,546
-DOES THAT MEAN IT'S OKAY
FOR US TO EAT HIM NOW?

568
00:22:23,579 --> 00:22:25,446
-I GOT DIBS ON THE BRAINS!

569
00:22:25,479 --> 00:22:27,012
-LET'S DIG IN!
-LET'S DIG IN!

570
00:22:31,979 --> 00:22:34,012
-AAH!
-AAH!

571
00:22:46,012 --> 00:22:49,046
-WHAT DO YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

572
00:22:52,099 --> 00:22:56,099
-[ SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

573
00:24:25,066 --> 00:24:27,099
-[ SIGHS ]

574
00:24:27,132 --> 00:24:30,132
[ WHISTLE! ]

575
00:24:33,932 --> 00:24:36,899
-MY NAME IS AKIM.
HOW ABOUT A RIDDLE?

576
00:24:36,932 --> 00:24:38,799
-OKAY,
WHAT PUNCH NEVER RUNS OUT,

577
00:24:38,832 --> 00:24:39,899
NO MATTER HOW MUCH YOU DRINK?

578
00:24:39,932 --> 00:24:41,766
-WHAT KIND OF RIDDLE IS THAT?

579
00:24:41,799 --> 00:24:43,699
-MY PUNCH! NOW STOP DODGING!

580
00:24:43,732 --> 00:24:46,399
-N-NEXT TIME ON BLOOD LAD,
"THAT'S FRIENDSHIP."

581
00:24:46,432 --> 00:24:49,166
-IN THE DEMON WORLD,
IT'S GOOD TO BE BAD.

